You can use this regular expression

    Startpoint: ([a-zA-Z0-9_]+)\n\nEndpoint: ([a-zA-Z0-9_]+)\n\nPath Type: [a-zA-Z0-9_]+\n+  Point +Incr +Path\n+  (?:[a-zA-Z0-9_()/ ]+ +(?:-?\d+\.\d{3} *[&amp;rf]? *){1,2} *\n+)*  slack \(VIOLATED\) +(-?\d.\d{3})

with [regex](https://en.cppreference.com/w/cpp/regex) to extract the values

